dct_description_sm: Map shows colony and protectorate. Colony is shown by hatched lines. Map shows provincial, district, and chiefdom boundaries, Sierra Leone Government railway, roads, provincial headquarters, districts, and other government stations. "W 404. B. WT 2i381A/116. 625. 2/23. J.W. Ltd." Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, map reproduction is attached to companion volume. Issued to accompany volume: Sierra Leone: report for 1921. Colonial reports - annual, no. 1150 (London: His Majesty's Stationery Office, 1923).
dct_creator_sm: Great Britain. His Majesty's Stationery Office
